#. VAR: āsavānañca → āsavānaṃ (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.106:6.7"
msgid "āsavānañca khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati; "
msgstr "And they realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements. "

msgctxt "an5.106:6.8"
msgid "ettāvatāpi kho, ānanda, bhikkhu saṃghe viharanto phāsuṃ vihareyya. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant could live comfortably while staying in a monastic community. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an5.106:7.1"
msgid "Imamhā cāhaṃ, ānanda, phāsuvihārā añño phāsuvihāro uttaritaro vā paṇītataro vā natthīti vadāmī”ti. "
msgstr "And I say that there is no better or finer way of living comfortably than this.” "

